---
import Button from './ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden bg-primary">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/962/1920/600" alt="Background" width="1920" height="600" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-10 mix-blend-overlay" />
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center text-white">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif mb-6 font-bold">Comece a sua jornada de saúde e bem-estar</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-bgLight/80 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
      Consulta ginecológica particular e com possibilidade de reembolso por convênio médico.
      O cuidado que você e sua família merecem.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <Button variant="accent" class="bg-[#25D366] text-white hover:bg-opacity-90 border-none shadow-lg">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        Agendar no WhatsApp
      </Button>
      <Button variant="outline" class="border-secondary text-secondary hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white shadow-lg">
        Localização
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
